  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the tandoor clay pot on medium heat for 5 minutes.",
    "Heat vegetable oil in the pot until shimmering.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic, sauté until onions are translucent.",
    "Stir in frozen peas and carrots, cook for 3 minutes until heated through.",
    "Add the cold jasmine rice, break up clumps, stir for 4 minutes, letting rice crisp slightly.",
    "Drizzle soy sauce, sprinkle salt and pepper, and mix thoroughly to coat the rice.",
    "Fold in vegan mayonnaise, stirring until the rice is evenly coated and creamy.",
    "Cover the pot, reduce heat to low, and cook for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Garnish with sliced green onions before serving."
